{"tid":2145644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯強烈譴責美國制裁中央與香港官員並稱毫無理據","createTime":"2020-08-08T06:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T08:01:41.000Z","uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e6890b2dc71dacf9abe73727afd1ac715506dda0","tid":2145644,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"民建聯發表聲明，強烈譴責美國政府制裁11名中央及香港官員及前官員，稱指控是毫無理據，任意妄為，目的是配合美國總統特朗普及反華政客，壓制中國發展的思路，並為特朗普個人選舉利益增加政治本錢。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯重申，任何國家都有維護國家主權、安全及領土完整的權利，各國亦普遍制訂國家安全立法以保護國家安全，香港各界和廣大市民歡迎及充分支持中央訂立制定「港區國安法」。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯批評，美國政府一而再地炒作香港議題，干涉香港事務及中國內政，惡言污衊「一國兩制」在本港有效運作的事實，以及破壞不干涉内政的國際關係準則，暴露出美國政府的霸權主義及雙重標準。<br />\n<br />\n好快到你哋DAB 唔洗咁心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542565-20200808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542565-20200808.htm&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=32313a3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542565-20200808.htm&h=c0905274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542565-20200808.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e68e36edb9d6e8b57c38085390afe36deb9a91a5","tid":2145644,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:06:41.000Z","msg":"成班只係識打咀炮....."},{"pid":"f7a28df1f3c2269cee8048d3ef921bd3e2cddd8c","tid":2145644,"uid":51546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"啲高官話好開心喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e410dbcf7964735220aad8f80761b5783a3b2b78","tid":2145644,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"反制未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a261053be7f55be0bf6177e0c67526545160688d","tid":2145644